|-
| $f3 xx yy || Set text position (x, y)
|-
| $f4 xx || Play sound effect xx
|-
| $f5 || Clear text window
|-
| $f6 nn || Insert item name #nn
|-
| $f7 nn || Insert character name #nn
|-
| $f8 || Insert player name
|-
| $fe || New line
|-
| $ff || End of string
